Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.03,0:21:53.29,Default,Souta,0,0,0,,Babičko?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.52,0:21:58.04,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,Omlouvám se. \NZdá se že nám malý {\i1}tanuki{\i0} dělá binec na poli.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.79,0:22:04.16,Default,Granny,0,0,0,,Dnes je akorát den na polívku z {\i1}tanukiho{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.16,0:22:05.46,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,Babi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.46,0:22:08.51,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,To nevadí. Vždyť je malý.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.43,0:22:11.31,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,Moc škody nenadělá.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.31,0:22:13.95,Default,Granny,0,0,0,,Kam ten mizera zmizel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.26,0:22:15.92,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,Moc se omlouvám!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.11,0:22:19.03,Default,Granny,0,0,0,,Jajoi, pojď!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.03,0:22:20.52,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,Babi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:42.73,Default,Souta,0,0,0,,Raz, dva...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.16,0:22:45.96,Default,Everyone,0,0,0,,Děkujeme!
